{"tid":2275457,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［所以唔救學生？］浸大校長錢大康：我每日都係辦公室睇幾個鐘Netflix 架！！","createTime":"2020-11-07T07:29:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T14:15:53.000Z","uid":22556,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a88398882c013d1789692342f13c91a1433e4115","tid":2275457,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:29:00.000Z","msg":"浸大昨晚舉行「全球大學電影獎2020」頒獎禮，多名電影界人士包括許鞍華、杜琪峰和張艾嘉等人出席。浸大校長錢大康在致辭時表示，雖然過去一年電影製作及戲院因疫情大受影響，但卻造就網上欣賞電影的風氣，他更打趣說，自己每日都會在辦公室觀看幾小時Netflix。<br />\n<br />\n錢大康亦大讚浸大學生在早前拍攝製作向前線醫護致敬的音樂錄像，並特別感謝黃秋生擔任今屆電影獎的大使。在頒獎時，錢大康笑言自己是許鞍華的粉絲，當晚和許鞍華一起頒發「亞洲劇情片」獎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1078679?fbclid=IwAR31146WhaiAbQMKJkRQO84H-cr3sS4Usv4GfNGaBN0trRuKohPfQgzj0ms\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1078679%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR31146WhaiAbQMKJkRQO84H-cr3sS4Usv4GfNGaBN0trRuKohPfQgzj0ms&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuNw%2Be0OQbTcODApWAJdetE8%3D&h=127a2d24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1078679%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR31146WhaiAbQMKJkRQO84H-cr3sS4Usv4GfNGaBN0trRuKohPfQgzj0ms&h=4bf60bee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1078679?fbclid=IwAR31146WhaiAbQMKJkRQO84H-cr3sS4Usv4GfNGaBN0trRuKohPfQgzj0ms</a>"},{"pid":"6c1a2e2470f506e1fc12899c3a64fc63cd390e94","tid":2275457,"uid":289900,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:32:35.000Z","msg":"我都想做校長啊<br />\n逗咁高人工就係喺office睇戲"},{"pid":"f563a1ede4feb981376ab4fd1f7463fb921ed226","tid":2275457,"uid":282637,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:52:50.000Z","msg":"食左誠實豆沙包?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"906ab6f75fd30dd1cc161dcca1bcb486996f401e","tid":2275457,"uid":220458,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:56:07.000Z","msg":"並特別感謝黃秋生擔任今屆電影獎的大使"},{"pid":"78d5e22f3822c40e13f790cab8f5393a54612dc4","tid":2275457,